content: Forward looking demand looks strong and we’re really encouraged with how kind of bookings look for us and so while some of that capacity has come out, we still see a pretty strong demand environment really across – across all of our markets into Hawaii from North America. The – in terms of the recovery, I don’t have that my fingertips what percent we were recovered in the first quarter, but it was still pretty dramatically off through most of the last several quarters up till this one, we were probably between 90% and 95% still missing from the market.
